extendedInfo.description: YumTable has innovated how you book restaurant tables and dine out, with hundreds of your favourite restaurants posting their available tables and last minute cancellations in real-time...all with great deals up to 50% off.Andriod App Features:- Over 800 Restaurants in Melbourne, Sydney and Hong Kong- Itâs free to book tables on YumTable directly from your Android Phone- Search live restaurant deals near you by time, cuisine & price- Bookings instantly confirmed- Restaurants know about you when you turn up â no annoying coupons!- View map directions and restaurant contact details- Share booking details with friends- Have a great time out!It's free to book a table with YumTable, and all bookings are instant and confirmed, with no phone calls and no more annoying coupons. Hungry diners can book these tables with a simple press of the button from our location-based iPhone/Android apps or the YumTable website. Find tables near you for right now, or where you are going to later in the day. Book for two people or book for a big group...and at all times get a great deal from up to 50% off breakfast, lunch or dinner bills and other enticements!Because restaurants regularly post their last minute tables and cancellations in real-time be sure to check back for great offers - weâre also adding new restaurants on every day. Please also suggest your favorite restaurant on our website and we'll look to getting them on-board.Thanks to all the support from hungry app downloaders and restaurants - please note that YumTable is currently servicing Melbourne and Sydney, Australia and Hong Kong.
